  Debt Freedom — Your Personal Debt Payoff Companion
                                                                                                                                                   
  Debt Freedom is an iOS app built for everyday Indians who want to take control of their finances and become debt-free. No sign-ups, no servers —
  everything stays on your device.                                                                                                                 
                                                                                                                                                 
  What It Does?                                                                                                                                    
                                                                                                                                                 
  You enter your income, expenses, loans, and assets. The app analyzes your financial health and generates a personalized month-by-month roadmap to
   pay off all your debt using proven strategies.                                                                                                
                                                                                                                                                   
  How It Works?                                                                                                                                    
   
  1. Financial Health Score                                                                                                                        
  The app calculates a score (5–95) based on your surplus ratio, loan risk, and interest rates. It tells you whether your situation is Critical, 
  Stressed, Tight, or Manageable — and exactly why.                                                                                                
                                                                                                                                                 
  2. Smart Debt Payoff Roadmap                                                                                                                     
  Using the Avalanche method, the app targets your most expensive debt first:                                                                    
  - Informal/moneylender loans (highest risk) → paid first                                                                                         
  - Credit card outstanding → paid next                                                                                                            
  - Then remaining loans sorted by interest rate (highest first)                                                                                   
                                                                                                                                                   
  As each loan closes, its freed EMI "snowballs" into the next target — accelerating your payoff.                                                  
                                                                                                                                                   
  3. Emergency Fund Tracking                                                                                                                       
  The app calculates how much emergency savings you need based on your employment type, dependents, and health insurance status. It splits your    
  surplus 50/50 between debt payoff and building your safety net until your fund is complete.                                                      
                                                                                                                                                 
  4. SIP Smart Pause                                                                                                                               
  If you have a monthly SIP (mutual fund investment) but also carry debt above 10% interest, the app recommends pausing the SIP and redirecting  
  that money to clear expensive debt first. Once high-interest debt is gone, your SIP resumes automatically — shown as a milestone in your roadmap.
                                                                                                                                                 
  Example:                                                                                                                                         
                                                                                                                                                 
  Harsh, 28, Contractual Employee, Ranchi                                                                                                          
  - Salary: ₹28,000/month                                                                                                                        
  - Expenses: ₹12,000/month                                                                                                                        
  - Loans: Moneylender (₹50K @ 48%), Bajaj EMI Card (₹30K @ 18%), Education Loan (₹1.2L @ 8.5%)                                                  
  - Savings: ₹18,000                                                                                                                               
                                                                                                                                                   
  What the app tells him? :                                                                                                                          
  - Health Score: Critical — negative pressure from moneylender debt                                                                               
  - Emergency Fund: ₹1.4L target, only ₹18K saved (0.77 months coverage)                                                                           
  - Roadmap: Moneylender closes by Month 5, Bajaj by Month 9, Education loan by Month 28                                                           
  - Each closure frees up EMI that speeds up the next payoff                                                                                       
                                                                                                                                                   
  Neha, 34, Government Employee, Jharkhand                                                                                                         
  - Salary: ₹65,000/month                                                                                                                          
  - Loans: SBI Personal (₹4L @ 12%), Gold Loan (₹1.5L @ 10%)                                                                                       
  - Gold: ₹5,00,000 | SIP: ₹10,000/month                                                                                                           
  - Health Insurance: ₹3L coverage                                                                                                                 
                                                                                                                                                   
  What the app tells her? :                                                                                                                          
  - Health Score: Manageable — stable government job, positive surplus                                                                             
  - Emergency Fund: Good (5.3 months coverage from gold + savings), but medical buffer added since insurance is below ₹5L                          
  - SIP paused temporarily — both loans are above 10%, so ₹10K/month redirected to debt                                                            
  - Roadmap: Gold loan clears by Month 8 → SIP resumes → SBI clears by Month 18                                                                    
                                                                                                                                                   
  Key Features                                                                                                                                     
                                                                                                                                                   
  - Completely offline — no account needed, all data stored locally on your phone                                                                  
  - Indian number formatting — amounts displayed as ₹1,40,400 (lakh/crore system)                                                                  
  - Accessible — VoiceOver support, Dynamic Type, 44×44pt tap targets                                                                              
  - Avalanche + Snowball hybrid — mathematically optimal payoff order with motivating milestone celebrations                                       
  - 120-month simulation — projects your entire debt-free journey with monthly breakdowns                                                          
  - Insurance-aware — health insurance status affects your emergency fund target                                                                   
  - Underwater loan detection — flags loans where your EMI doesn't even cover monthly interest                                                     
                                                                                                                                                   
